name: Load HuggingFace Dataset
description: Load any dataset from the HuggingFace Hub with streaming support and preview the first rows.

name: Tokenizer Setup & Encoding
description: Load a pre-trained tokenizer from HuggingFace, encode/decode text, and inspect token IDs.

name: Text Classification Pipeline
description: Run zero-shot or fine-tuned text classification using a HuggingFace pipeline in just a few lines.

name: Text Generation with LLM
description: Generate text completions using a causal language model from HuggingFace.

name: PyTorch Neural Network
description: Define, train, and evaluate a simple feedforward neural network with PyTorch on synthetic data.

name: LoRA Fine-tuning Setup
description: Set up LoRA (Low-Rank Adaptation) for parameter-efficient fine-tuning with PEFT and Transformers.

name: TensorFlow / Keras Model
description: Build and train a Keras Sequential model for binary classification with TensorFlow.

name: Scikit-learn ML Pipeline
description: Build a complete ML pipeline with preprocessing, training, and evaluation using scikit-learn.

name: Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
description: Quick EDA template with Pandas profiling: shape, dtypes, missing values, correlations, and distributions.

name: Data Cleaning & Transformation
description: Common data cleaning operations: handle missing values, remove duplicates, type casting, and text normalization.

name: Model Evaluation Metrics
description: Compute and display accuracy, precision, recall, F1, confusion matrix, and ROC-AUC for a classifier.

name: GPU & Environment Check
description: Detect available GPUs (CUDA/MPS), check PyTorch and TensorFlow versions, and display system info.

name: Weights & Biases Logging
description: Set up experiment tracking with W&B: initialize a run, log metrics, and finish the session.

name: Environment Setup & Imports
description: Common pip installs and imports for ML/AI projects: torch, transformers, datasets, pandas, numpy.

name: Upload Model to HuggingFace Hub
description: Push a trained model and tokenizer to the HuggingFace Hub for sharing or deployment.

name: Image Classification (ResNet)
description: Fine-tune a ResNet model for image classification using torchvision and a custom dataset.

name: YOLO Object Detection
description: Run YOLOv8 object detection on images using Ultralytics.

name: Image Generation (Stable Diffusion)
description: Generate images with Stable Diffusion using the HuggingFace Diffusers library.

name: Vision Transformer (ViT) Fine-tuning
description: Fine-tune a Vision Transformer for image classification with HuggingFace Transformers.

name: Image Segmentation (SAM)
description: Segment objects in images using Meta's Segment Anything Model.

name: Image Data Augmentation
description: Apply augmentations with Albumentations for training robust vision models.

name: Whisper Speech-to-Text
description: Transcribe audio to text using OpenAI's Whisper model.

name: Audio Classification
description: Classify audio samples using a HuggingFace audio classification pipeline.

name: Text-to-Speech (TTS)
description: Generate speech from text using Coqui TTS or Bark.

name: Text Summarization
description: Summarize long documents using a HuggingFace summarization pipeline.

name: Named Entity Recognition (NER)
description: Extract entities (person, org, location) from text using a NER pipeline.

name: Text Embeddings (Sentence-BERT)
description: Generate semantic text embeddings for similarity search, clustering, or RAG.

name: Question Answering
description: Extract answers from context passages using a QA pipeline.

name: Machine Translation
description: Translate text between languages using Helsinki-NLP models.

name: QLoRA 4-bit Fine-tuning
description: Fine-tune large LLMs in 4-bit quantization with QLoRA, fitting on consumer GPUs.

name: DPO / Preference Training
description: Train models with Direct Preference Optimization using TRL.

name: Distributed Training (Multi-GPU)
description: Set up distributed training across multiple GPUs with PyTorch DDP or Accelerate.

name: Mixed Precision Training
description: Speed up training with FP16/BF16 mixed precision using PyTorch AMP.

name: Axolotl Fine-tuning Config
description: Generate an Axolotl YAML config for fine-tuning LLMs with LoRA, QLoRA, or full fine-tuning.

name: ONNX Model Export
description: Export a PyTorch model to ONNX format for production deployment.

name: Gradio Demo App
description: Build a quick interactive demo for your model with Gradio.

name: vLLM Inference Server
description: Serve LLMs with vLLM for high-throughput, low-latency inference.

name: Model Quantization (GPTQ/AWQ)
description: Quantize large models to 4-bit for faster inference with GPTQ or AWQ.

name: BLEU & ROUGE Scores
description: Compute BLEU and ROUGE scores for text generation and summarization evaluation.

name: Perplexity Evaluation
description: Measure language model perplexity on a text corpus.

name: LLM Benchmark Suite
description: Run common LLM benchmarks: MMLU, HellaSwag, ARC using lm-eval.

name: Streaming Large Datasets
description: Stream terabyte-scale datasets without downloading them entirely.

name: Batch Tokenization Pipeline
description: Tokenize an entire dataset efficiently for training with map and batching.

name: Parquet Data Processing
description: Read, write, and query Parquet files for efficient data storage.

name: MLflow Experiment Tracking
description: Track experiments, parameters, metrics, and artifacts with MLflow.

name: Reproducibility Setup
description: Set all random seeds for reproducible ML experiments across NumPy, PyTorch, and TensorFlow.
